    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describes objects, particularly tools, machines, or components, that change position relative to other objects or components within the same object, or relative to a coordinate system.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
